From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mohammad Ebrahim Rahimbeiky <rahimbeiky@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 22 Jun 2026 22:00:00 +0400
Subject: [PATCH] Add combat knockback profile config and command

Adds a dedicated reloadable combat profile at knockback/profile.yml, its
reload command, and the fail-safe profile loader. Runtime NMS wiring is kept
in an earlier patch so later PandaSpigot patches still apply cleanly.

